            "title": "科倫博泰折讓7.58%配股籌19.64億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科倫博泰(06990)公布，擬配售591.8萬股集資19.64億元，配股價331.8元，較昨收市價359元折讓7.58%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：科倫博泰官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_06990-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：科倫博泰官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240508_FI_source-web_06990-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：科倫博泰官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收價328.88元比較，配股價較之有0.89%溢價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今次配股集資所得淨額估計約19.43億元，其中約80%用於產品研發、臨床試驗、註冊備案、製造及商業化；約15%用於提升內部研發技術能力、加強外部合作及拓展產品管線組合；約5%用於補充營運資金及作一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14985218-%e7%a7%91%e5%80%ab%e5%8d%9a%e6%b3%b0%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%937-58%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c19-64%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
